task: Record an audio clip using Audio Recorder app and save it.

action.description: Tap the "RECORD" button to start recording an audio clip.
Tap the "STOP" button to stop the recording.
Tap the "FINISH" button to save the recorded audio clip.
Tap the "Save" button to save the recorded audio clip.
